Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事隔八年看见哥哥的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是杀人者的嘴脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我也是同样的嘴脸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的Freyja真的是你发射的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 原本打算阻止哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便杀死哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能把Freyja 把这Damocles的钥匙交给哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算被哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用了GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对娜娜莉使用GEASS?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我期望过无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.27,0:01:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕只让娜娜莉重见光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 王者的力量 绝对服从的GEASS也无法对娜娜莉使用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那现在呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再扭曲娜娜莉的意志 我就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RE;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 无论如何都要阻挠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 我误会了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为作法不同 你也在以你的方式为日本着想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和鲁路修有必须完成的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 这么想要力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不该留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击败你 阻止鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你如愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利瓦尔不去逃难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能和大家每天过得开心就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有主君的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是依靠着谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脆弱的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去 您这伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须为起始的责任负责
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为领导者的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥没有掌握这个世界的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自称ZERO践踏人意志的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就该继续逃亡生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要终日为逃避暗杀而奔波的未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了你的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么时候恳求过那种事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要和哥哥在一起生活就足够
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现实被各种因素所支配
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抗争是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 才作为反抗组织战斗至今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理应也有组织中实现的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些无法加入组织和系统的人该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在怎么能断言这是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别居高临下教训人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能进入组织的人该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓正义…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果服从侵略者的做法 就等于承认他们的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是现在出击会死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就算这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只懂得这种活法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要还有必须保护之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:06:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许失去了对战争应有的矜持与美学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便这样也必须有容身处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为此战斗到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直人 我们这样做对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但人称战争是发明之母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不承认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布丁伯爵没有看到人在其中的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫妮娜来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么说?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是尽自己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想重蹈覆辙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但人是脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 有梦想错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我连这资格都没吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明还能干下去 能干下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么大家都看不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见了 看到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抗争就是人类的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人和世界是如此难以如人所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就想人家都听你的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是卑劣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扭曲人心 践踏人尊严的GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那Damocles又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强制令人俯首称臣的系统 就不卑劣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damocles会成为仇恨的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仇恨会汇集于此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让大家能迎接明天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 娜娜莉你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修．V．布里塔尼亚下令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Damocles的钥匙给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能交给哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再 罪上加罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍小聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纪录完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纪录下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰雷米亚．哥特瓦尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带给你败北的 有纪念意义的男人之名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纪念? 那和我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我没有记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动起来 Tristan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕只能飞也好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下辐射波动也用尽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护盾能量也耗完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢不了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连GEASS的诅咒都用上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 如此强大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是这边的规格比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 有这样的力量 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束吧 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果有正义的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 没打到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你打到了 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 你赢了 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经在靠自己的意志活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也能走自己的路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用了吧 GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥是恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑劣 无耻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…太过分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛者枢木朱雀已败
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无意求生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了那位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐耶 你最近才得知鲁路修的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这又如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却理解他的一部分本质
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是神圣布里塔尼亚帝国皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修．V．布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 鲁路修使用了Freyja代表…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈泽尔已加入我麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:12:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至此 Damocles与Freyja也全部为我所用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑骑士团不再拥有与我对抗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也要垂死挣扎的话 招待你们的只会是Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无人能阻我霸业
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 今天这一瞬间 世界已陷落我手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修．V．布里塔尼亚下令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界啊 臣服于我吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神圣布里塔尼亚帝国第99代唯一皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:13:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼黑骑士团C.E.O. 超合众国第2代最高评议会议长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修．V．布里塔尼亚陛下出现在我们眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反对鲁路修陛下的愚昧之徒 正被送往刑场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次大战中 帝都Pendragon和众多将士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括Knight of Zero枢木朱雀卿在内 付出了惨重的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,E.U.批准超合众国宪章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的鲁路修陛下 终于实现了世界统一伟业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光荣与鲁路修陛下同在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单纯的独裁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反抗者全部被杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 被人听到的话会满门抄斩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然不得不把这种内容作为正义报导
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 这就是你想做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支配世界和人们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时何必与鲁路修顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为迎来明天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算重复着成功与失败也必须前行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人和科学是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是进化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是进步 布丁伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在记恨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你猜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊德先生和拉克夏塔以前发生过什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是些琐碎的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想想根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在出去正中他们下怀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人 鲁路修在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道鲁路修他们策划的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开枪 我来对付他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 假面骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 按约定你来杀死我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:16:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按预定 世界的仇很正集中在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我消失 就能斩断这仇恨的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑骑士团留有ZERO的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈泽尔也会听命于ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样世界将不再用军事力量 而是在谈判桌上就能解决
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能朝明天前进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零之镇魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在C的世界中 我们明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们期望着明天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得愿望和GEASS很像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠自己无法实现的事会寻求他人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:17:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就对所有人使用名为愿望的GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了世界的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 你作为对人使用GEASS的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有被杀的觉悟 才有资格开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 你要成为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从世界的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝鲁路修．V．布里塔尼亚手中拯救世界的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁…鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对你来说也是惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:18:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须作为正义的使者戴着面具活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再是枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也必须为世界牺牲常人该有的幸福 永远
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份GEASS 我确实收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…哥哥之前都是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…毁灭世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造…世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睁开眼睛 哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔王鲁路修已死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,释放人质
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂且撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道那是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍赖 我有哥哥就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:20:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有哥哥的明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后世界好了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:21:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用在战争上的能源 现在用在饥饿与贫困
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种仇恨与罪名都被被你一手包办了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家比起Damocles这个系统 更容易记住一个有名有姓的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够可笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 正因为如此 大家才不会被过去束缚 能继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又会笑着说“如我所料”了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然还留下了各种问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名为GEASS的王的力量 会令人孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好像不太对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.97,0:22:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 鲁路修
